{"type":"text","timestamp":1781761473365,"sessionID":"ses_126bf8e4fffelWjiibhoiChLwm","part":{"id":"prt_ed94278bd001IZUSEvr85StUoF","messageID":"msg_ed942634e0013lcidnKCtcPH6Z","sessionID":"ses_126bf8e4fffelWjiibhoiChLwm","type":"text","text":"The atomic save helper promotes the pending file after `indexPrepared` succeeds. I’m checking its caller to determine whether DB writes happen before promotion and whether failures are rolled back.","time":{"start":1781761472701,"end":1781761473363},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_000378d61980f8ad016a3385c0af908191a362bfc2aef151be","phase":"commentary"}}}}
